    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td> Media relations</td>
      <td> Identify key reporters and bloggers. Develop specific messages for each reporter.</td>
      <td> Unique stories.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td> Analyst relations</td>
      <td> Track key analysts in market. Review reports and media commentary.</td>
      <td> Analyst briefings. Inclusion in analyst reports.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td> Speaking</td>
